room_title: Escape room "Espionage" by Break Out! in Cedar Rapids
review: This is my favorite place to have a fun night with friends. I have done a bachlorette party here, girls night, and friends night out. I have done all the rooms, POW, Taken, Child's play, Time to die, and last night Espionage!!! Can't wait to come back and try again and actually break out of Espionage!
